Interface ObjectContainerSpec

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExtObjectContainer, InternalObjectContainer, ObjectContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientObjectContainer, ExternalObjectContainer, IoAdaptedObjectContainer, LocalObjectContainer, ObjectContainerBase, ObjectContainerSession, TransportObjectContainer
    public interface ObjectContainerSpec
extends InternalObjectContainer
    Workaround to provide the Java 5 version with a hook to add ExtObjectContainer. (Generic method declarations won't match ungenerified YapStreamBase implementations otherwise and implementing it directly kills .NET conversion.)
